ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent codes which identify injectable factor Xa inhibitors, which are used for venous thromboembolism (VTE) prophylaxis.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Medication. The intent of this data element is to identify patients who are on a select injectable factor Xa inhibitor as prophylaxis for VTE. ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with injectable factor Xa inhibitor medications. These are RxNorm codes.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
